name: Workshop Restaurant

reviews.review_text: Amazing food. Ambience was also brilliant. Starters were savoury specially the Chilly Prawns, Golden Fried squids, Butter Garlic Squids and Apple Chicken. Good variety of cocktails and mocktails. The special Thali is something worthwhile and filling. Had a good time in a long while.

Nice place for locals to hangout we dropped in for snacks n soup late evening ordered seafood chowder it was nice. Grilled shrimps, Madagascar prawns something like thermidor prawns it was nice. Southern fried chicken it was crispy and cheese garlic fries. Red velvet ice-cream.

You won't be disappointed,  hospitable staff although service was bit slow cos everything is prepared fresh.

They have a another place in Porvorim near the court will try as we were told some dishes which are served there are not served at this joint n vice-versa.

Ambience 3/5
Hospitality 4/5
Food 4/5
Price 4/5

Will visit one more time after visiting Porvorim joint.

Cozy place located at Tonca. Warm ambience.

We had squid butter garlic (creamy and tasty).

The coriander chicken was juicy, succulent and delicious (and I don't use these three words together often). Was really good.

For dessert we wanted darsan with ice cream, which was sold out. Turned out to be a blessing for us because they recommended their home churned red velvet cake ice cream, which blew our minds away. It was really heavenly and a great way to end the day!! Would highly recommend it.

A pleasant dining experience!!

description:
**Dining Delight at Workshop Restaurant**

Nestled in the charming neighborhood of Caranzalem, Workshop Restaurant boasts an impressive 4.5-star rating from nearly 1,900 enthusiastic diners. Known for its wide array of offerings encapsulated in popular tags like "service" (52 mentions), "thali" (43 mentions), "Goan" (23 mentions), and "prawns" (11 mentions), this culinary haven is a must-visit for both locals and tourists alike.

**Ambiance & Design**

Walking into Workshop Restaurant, you are instantly enveloped by a warm and cozy atmosphere that invites relaxation and enjoyment. Reviewers have described the ambiance as "brilliant," with photos showcasing a tasteful blend of contemporary decor and rustic charm, featuring soft lighting that highlights the culinary creations. The space is thoughtfully designed to create a welcoming environment that’s ideal for casual hangouts or celebratory meals. Picture diners reveling in delightful conversation against a backdrop of tasteful art—a visual treat supported by images revealing the restaurant’s inviting interiors.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The culinary offerings at Workshop are nothing short of exceptional. Signature dishes like the **Chilly Prawns** and **Butter Garlic Squids** frequently steal the show, with patrons praising their savory nature and perfect execution. The seafood chowder has also garnered attention for its rich and comforting flavor, while the **special thali** has been highlighted as both filling and worthwhile, offering a delicious snapshot of Goan cuisine. The presentation of each dish is visually enticing, enhancing the overall dining experience. To round off the meal, dessert options such as the home-churned **red velvet cake ice cream** have left diners raving about their heavenly taste, ensuring a sweet ending to any meal. Dietary considerations appear well accommodated, with ample choices for both sea lovers and land enthusiasts alike.

**Customer Experience & Service**

The experience at Workshop Restaurant is defined by its attentive and hospitable staff, who are dedicated to creating a memorable dining outing. Customers have noted that although service might occasionally be a touch slow—attributed to the commitment to freshly prepared dishes—it remains friendly and efficient. Whether you choose to make a reservation or stroll in for a meal, the staff is always eager to assist, making each visit an enjoyable affair.

**Popularity & Reviews**

Workshop Restaurant has quickly become a favorite among local foodies, generating a buzz through vibrant social media channels. With its high rating reflective of well-rounded reviews, the restaurant has captured the hearts of many. Critics and customers alike have applauded its diverse menu and friendly atmosphere, further solidifying its reputation as a hotspot. The mention of another location in Porvorim opens exciting possibilities for culinary exploration, as diners expressed eagerness to try dishes unique to that spot.

**Utilizing Visual Content**

The visual representation supports every delightful word about Workshop Restaurant; from the scrumptious dishes, like the beautifully plated **Golden Fried Squids**, to the ambient interior that fosters a warm vibe, each photograph captures the essence of the dining experience. The impressive food styling in the images speaks volumes about the care taken in crafting each dish, adding a dedicated touch that enhances the overall joy of dining. 

In summary, Workshop Restaurant is a culinary gem that promises an unforgettable experience through its delightful menu, welcoming atmosphere, and attentive service. Whether you're indulging in scrumptious seafood or savoring a vibrant thali, you are bound to leave with a smile and a full heart—along with the desire to return.
